nodes.bodyText: If you want to eventually pass in other secrets for things that are static resources you might need to add some more secrets and pass them similar to https://github.com/Azure/azure-sdk-for-java/blob/master/sdk/keyvault/tests.yml#L21.

nodes.bodyText: Thanks Wes, we've decided to hold off on using static resources for now until there is a better long-term solution.  Live SMS tests will not be part of automation for now.
